(101, 'Panamed Face Mask Earloop', 'jp-0601202121-PPI-Panamed-Face-Mask-Ear-Loop-(2).jpg', '&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/PanamedFaceMaskEarloop_3.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;200px&quot; style=&quot;cursor: default;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;A disposable device that creates a physical barrier between the mouth and nose of the wearer and the potential contaminants in the immediate environment.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Key Features:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Constructed from 3ply polypropylene spun-bonded non-woven material that provides dependable protection&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Soft loop ties ensure comfort and secure fitting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ultrasonically-welded loop ties provide maximum durability&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Adaptable nose bar for secure fitting&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Highly breathable&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fiberglass-free and hypoallergenic&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Provides superior comfort and protection&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;BFE &ge;95%&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;YYT 0969-2013 compliant&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Meets the W.H.O. Technical Specifications for PPE&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/dC0Hga10nbk&quot; width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;allowfullscreen&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 22),
(102, 'Panamed Nanofiber KN95 Respirator', '23042020175937K95Respirator_2.jpg', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Clinical Application:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Respirator mask that provides superior protection against vapors, mists, dust pollen, blood, and other harmful infectious pathogens. This mask uses a nanofiber microporous membrane material which not only meets the national standard for a medical protective mask in key indicators such as filtration performance and blood penetration resistance but also in environmental and corrosion resistance. The filtration rate of this mask reaches and even exceeds the N95 level, which ensures safe and reliable use.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Features and Benefits:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Patented Nanofiber Filter Technology guarantees filtration efficiency against blood penetration, vapors, mists, and airborne infectious agents. Filters 95% of particles of 0.3&mu;m in size&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The mask is cut in 3D with an M-shaped nose clip, fits for almost any facial size/shape, ensuring good sealing performance.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mask surface is made from high-quality cotton and non-woven fabric, non-irritating, and hypo-allergenic.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Four-layer fresh air technology&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Cost economical can be reused for up to 20 times&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ear loop design with adjustable buckle for easy, safe, and secure wearing.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lightweight and breathable&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Individually packed in resealable pouch: clean and hygienic prevent contamination.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;GB2626-2006, Standards equivalent to NIOSH N95/FFP2&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Multi-Layer Nano-filtration Protection with Fresh Air Technology:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Non-woven protection layer: prevents infiltration of mist and water vapor;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Meltblown electrostatic cotton: effectively isolates fine dust particles;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Nanofiber membrane: can filter out 95% particles of 0.3&mu;m in size&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Non-stick non-woven support layer: sweat and oil absorption, skin-friendly, and comfortable.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 0, 22),
(103, 'MC Closed Suction Catheter', '19052020153344MCClosedSuctionSystem.jpg', '&lt;b&gt;Clinical Application:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;This closed system suction catheter allows safe suctioning of secretions and continuous ventilation even during suctioning. It is designed to prevent VAP, PEEP loss, nosocomial infection and cross-contamination.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Features and Benefits:&lt;/b&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n 	&lt;li&gt;Double-swivel elbow connector to provide patient comfort&lt;/li&gt;\r\n 	&lt;li&gt;Frosted catheter with atraumatic tip, reducing mucosal\r\ndamage.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n 	&lt;li&gt;Catheter markings to assist with the depth of insertion.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n 	&lt;li&gt;With MDI port for drug delivery.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n 	&lt;li&gt;Flushing port for cleaning of the catheter.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n 	&lt;li&gt;Isolation valve to prevent PEEP loss and for effective flushing\r\nof the catheter.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n 	&lt;li&gt;100% sealed connection to prevent cross-contamination and\r\nthe spread of infection.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n 	&lt;li&gt;Color-coded for size identification&lt;/li&gt;\r\n 	&lt;li&gt;72 hours maximum usage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n 	&lt;li&gt;With day sticker for replacement guide&lt;/li&gt;\r\n 	&lt;li&gt;Latex Free and DEHP-Free&lt;/li&gt;\r\n 	&lt;li&gt;Catheter length: 550mm&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 15),
