(120, 'MC Video Laryngoscope', 'jp-1109202008-MC-Video-Laryngoscope-and-MC-Disposable-Blade-1-ppi.jpg', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Clinical Application:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;A convenient and durable video display tandem with &lt;br&gt;disposable blade, engineered to provide confidence,&lt;br&gt;precise and successful endotracheal intubation. This device&lt;br&gt;uses a camera technology that provides high quality laryngeal&lt;br&gt;visualization, which enables clinicians to perform smooth&lt;br&gt;intubation, while minimizing soft tissue manipulation.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Key Features:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Designed for clinical use in any situations, especially during\r\nemergency intubation.\r\nResponsive and easy to use 3.5&rdquo; intuitive touchscreen with\r\nadjustable LED source and display luminosity. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;HD image viewing with automatic focusing and anti-fog\r\ntechnology guarantees optimal visual capability. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Real time recording of video sequence and still image\r\ncapture. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Portable and waterproof &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Provides improve patient care with the use of sterile single-use\r\nblades, which eliminates the risk of cross-contamination. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;With comprehensive range of Macintosh blades for different\r\ntypes of patients. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Suitable for infants, children, adults, obese as well as\r\ndifficult-to-intubate patients. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Anti-fog blade and camera &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;MC Laryngoscope is packed in a small case which contains:\r\none adapter, one cable and one laryngoscope blade.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', 1, 7),
(121, 'Unimex Super Absorbent Polymer (SAP)', 'jp-1409202014-PPI-Unimex-SAP-(1).jpg', '&lt;div&gt;Designed to absorb fluid hundreds of time of its own weight in a short period of time. Used for prevention of spills and for safe management of liquid clinical waste.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;FEATURES AND BENEFITS:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Converts fluid into reduced odor gel for easy handling and disposal.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Reduces hospital-acquired infection by reducing free air particles.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Plays an integral part of infection prevention system.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;One 6 gram sachet absorbs 100-200 times its own weight.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Packed in water-soluble sachets.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;by 100&#039;s&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 18);
