(124, 'Unimex Latex Disposal Gloves', 'jp-1509202013-PPI-PIS-PIS-Unimex-Latex-Examination-Gloves-F-ppi.jpg', '&lt;div&gt; Used to provide hand protection during medical\r\nexaminations and procedures for prevention of cross contamination.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;FEATURES AND BENEFITS:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Made from high-quality natural latex material. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Strictly standardized for medical use. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Odorless and Powder-free&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ambidextrous&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', 1, 18),
(125, 'Unimex Anti-Embolism Stocking', 'jp-1509202015-PPI-PIS_Unimex_Anti-Embolism-Stocking-ppi.jpg', '&lt;div&gt;Used to promote increased\r\nblood flow velocity in the legs and it is clinically proven to reduce the\r\nrisk of venous thromboembolism. It also prevents the damaging\r\neffects of venous distension that occurs during surgery and hospitalization.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;FEATURES AND BENEFITS:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;High compression to improve blood circulation in the leg vein. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Applies the clinically proven pressure pattern of 15-20mmHg. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Stockings are made of 80% nylon and 20% spandex, designed\r\nto provide comfort and coolness during use. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;With inspection hole &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Color-coded on heel area for easy size identification. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Suitable for standing all day work, bedridden patient and\r\nairplane ride. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Single patient use &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Available in Knee and Thigh length&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Available in four different sizes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 18),
(126, 'Sedasenz Subglottic Endotracheal Tube', 'jp-1609202013-Sedasenz-Endotracheal-Tube-with-Subglottic-Port-F-1-ppi.jpg', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;A special type of ETT with suction line \r\nintegrated above the cuff, intended to eliminate secretions from the subglottic \r\narea, specifically designed to prevent Ventilator Associated Pneumonia \r\n(VAP) in long term intubated patients.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Features and Advantage:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Subglottic Port secures removal of subglottic secretions to decrease risk of VAP using syringe or suction equipment.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Rounded bullnose tip with Murphy eye is smoothly formed to avoid \r\nvocal cord damage and to ensure atraumatic and smooth intubation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;HVLP cuff design to provide effective sealing and increase pressure distribution.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Double marking to guide intubation by laryngoscope to help ensure accurate placement&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Radiopaque x-ray line facilitates verification of tube placement.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Available Sizes: &lt;/b&gt;7.0, 7.5 and 8.0&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 7),
(127, 'Respisenz Breathing Circuit for Ventilator', 'jp-2109202013-Respisenz-Ventilator-Circuit-PPI.jpg', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;b&gt;CLINICAL APPLICATION:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Assembly of components which connects the patient&rsquo;s airway to the mechanical ventilator providing oxygen to a patient who is physically unable to breath or is breathing insufficiently.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;FEATURES AND BENEFITS:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bicolored corrugated tubings, allowing identification of either the inspiratory or the expiratory limb.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Standard connectors to fit with most ventilators and humidifiers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Flexible and lightweight&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;With available options to accommodate different patient requirement&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1.8 meter breathing circuit adult manifold&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Available Variants:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Respisenz Breathing Circuit for Ventilator with Water Trap (Adult)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Respisenz Breathing Circuit for Ventilator with Neb (Adult)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Respisenz Breathing Circuit for Ventilator Universal (Adult&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 15),
(128, 'Respisenz Manual Resuscitator', 'jp-2109202013-PPI-PIS-Respisenz-Manual-Resuscitator-F2-ppi.jpg', '&lt;div&gt;CLINICAL APPLICATION:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;A hand-held device use to manually ventilate apneic patients, also use for spontaneously breathing patients to augment ventilation and/or oxygen delivery.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;FEATURES AND BENEFITS:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Made from medical grade PVC, allows fast recoil time for rapid ventilation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Clear mask with cushion provides comfort by preventing pressure points to the patient&#039;s face.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy assembling and disassembling, time saving&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Equipped with pressure relief valve for easy adjustment of pressure requirement.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ISO standard connectors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Available in Pre-Assembled type which provides dependability during emergency situations.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;3 sizes available: Adult, Pedia, Neonate&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 15),
(129, 'Vitromed Tissue Embedding Medium', 'jp-2509202008-PMC-PIS_Vitromed-Tissue-Embedding-Medium-F-img1-ppi.jpg', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Recommended for all general tissue embedding and sectioning use.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;FEATURES and BENEFITS:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Made from highly purified histological paraffin wax, developed to \r\nprovide exceptional tissue penetration and excellent quality sections.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pellet\r\n form of paraffin wax gives it remarkable handling capabilities for \r\nusers and quicker melting characteristics at melting point of 54-57&deg;C.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Dissects\r\n neatly and smoothly with serial sections of 4 microns and is proven to \r\nmaintain premium quality ribbon continuity while ensuring virtually no \r\ncracks or crumbling.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 11),
(131, 'Sedasenz Pre-loaded Endotracheal Tube', 'jp-2809202013-Sedasenz-Pre-Loaded-Endotracheal-Tube.jpg', '&lt;div&gt;Integrated endotracheal tube and stylet in one for fast set-up and \r\nconvenience, designed to achieve successful emergency intubation.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;FEATURES AND BENEFITS:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;15mm Connector provides universal fitting to the breathing circuits, resuscitators, closed suction catheters etc.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Thermosensitive material conforms to patient&rsquo;s body temperature, reducing trauma to the patient&rsquo;s tissue.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Kink-resistant shaft allows continuous air flow.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Radiopaque line allows verification of tube placement. Guarantees \r\neasy and accurate identification of tube placement during x-ray.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Responsive pilot balloon allows visual identification of the cuff&rsquo;s intcgrity.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Inflation line is smoothly connected to the shaft, can effectively withstand pulling forces.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Smooth cuff-to-shaft transition, no sharp edges on the sleeve area, ensures atraumatic insertion.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Double line marking facilitates accurate cuff placement below the vocal cord.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Volume Low Pressure (HVLP) Cuff provides ideal pressure \r\ndistribution and effective seal, reducing risk of vocal cord injury and \r\ntracheal damage.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Murphy eye at the tip meant to increase safety by ensuring that \r\nadequate ventilation is maintained even if the tip of the tube was fixed\r\n to the tracheal wall or occluded by secretions.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bullnose tip&lt;b&gt;, r&lt;/b&gt;ounded beveled tip reduces risk of damage to the tissues during intubation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Stylet has a low friction coating to facilitate smooth withdrawal, with a soft distal tip to reduce the risk of mucosal damage&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 7),
(132, 'De Royal Suction Liner', 'jp-0110202010-De-Royal-Safeliner-Canisers-Semi-rigid-System-F-1-ppi.jpg', '&lt;div&gt;Disposable suction collecting canisters, especially made for\r\nhealthcare facilities to provide cost effective solution in\r\nhandling and disposal of medical waste for effective\r\ninfection control management.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;FEATURES AND BENEFITS:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Provides simple yet innovatively safe fluid waste management. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Promotes safe handling of medical waste fluid, improves infection control practice. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Protects hospital investment due to it&#039;s innovative filter. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Adhesive seal on lid keeps lid securely in place to\r\nhelp prevent leakage and spills once full, spill-safe for clinicians.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Self-aligning lid allows quick and easy lid assembly.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Innovative filter technology helps prevent backflow of\r\naspirated fluid into the vacuum system. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Improved flow rates allow greater suction power in clinical\r\nsettings. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Canisters are nested for efficient packaging and easy storage. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Available Sizes:\r\n 3 liters for large volume suctioning\r\n 1.5 liter ideal for ICU&rsquo;s, ER and wards&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 14);
