(134, 'Panacan IV Cannula', 'jp-0610202008-Panamed-PIS-Panacan-IV-Cannula-ppi.jpg', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Used to provide access to the peripheral vascular system for the administration of fluids and drugs or for withdrawal of blood.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;FEATURES AND BENEFITS:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Panacan FEP standard catheter is tapered and siliconized which offers high resistance to kinking.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;It features very minimum resistance during insertion, therefore less traumatic to the patient.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;It has flexible, easy grip wings that aid in simple and safe fixation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;With radiopaque line for placement confirmation during X-ray.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table width=&quot;720&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;456&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;TYPES:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;264&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;SIZES:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;456&quot;&gt;Panacan IV Cannula with Wing&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;264&quot;&gt;G- 18, 20, 22, 24, 26&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;456&quot;&gt;Panacan IV Cannula with Wing and Port&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;264&quot;&gt;G- 18, 20, 22, 24, 26&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 26),
(136, 'KN95-H Particulate Respirator', 'jp-0710202009-Panamed-KN95-H-Particulate-Respirator-(1).jpg', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(109, 109, 109); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: medium; letter-spacing: normal;&quot;&gt;Five layer respiratory protection against airborne bacteria, viruses, dust, fumes and droplets. Designed with adjustable over the head strap for comfort fit and better seal.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(109, 109, 109); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: medium; letter-spacing: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Features and Advantage:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;font-family: Lato, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1.41575em 3em; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style: disc; color: rgb(109, 109, 109); font-size: medium; letter-spacing: normal; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Provides low breathing resistance with high filtration efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;With ultrasonically welded, adjustable head strap that allows&lt;br style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;better fit.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Adjustable nosepiece for custom seal.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Particle Filtration Efficiency (PFE) against non-oily particles &ge;95%&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Bacterial Filtration Efficiency (BFE) &ge;95%&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Comfortable 3D flex design allows ease of breathing.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Free of odor and stimulation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Underwent ultrasonically welding process for comfortable&lt;br style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;weari