(142, 'Unimex Silicone Duodenal Tube', 'jp-1610202012-Square-batch-2-(2).png', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Unimex Silicone Duodenal Tube is used for nasogastric introduction for administration of enteral nutrition or for aspiration of intestinal fluids.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;FEATURES AND BENEFITS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;100% silicone material&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Cap on funnel, prevents bacteria from entering the tube&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Markings on the tube to determine the depth of insertion&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;With radio opaque line and tip&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; colo