(180, 'ELECTRIC PATIENT BED W/ IV STAND, 5 FUNCTION', 'jp-0212202016-Electric-Patient-Bed-with-iv-stand-5-function.png', '&lt;div&gt;Provides the ultimate comfort level by allowing a multitude of adjustable positions. The last 2 positions allow the patient to be in a trendelenburg position.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;FEATURES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Overall Length&amp;nbsp; 217 cm&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Overall Width 98 cm&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lowest Height 35 cm (Floor to Bed base)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Highest Height 78 cm (Floor to Bed base)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Back Raise Angle 0&deg; to 70&deg;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Leg Raise Angle 0&deg; to 40&deg;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tilt Angle 0&deg; to 10&deg;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mattress Length 200 cm&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Mattress Width 90 cm Mattress&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Height 10 cm&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Safe Working Load 160 kg&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;With 5 controls, the bed is able to perform the following base functions:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://rainbowcare.com.sg/image/catalog/products/beds/function1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Function 1&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; display: block; border-radius: 3px; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;BACK RAISE&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http:/