(181, 'ELECTRIC PATIENT BED W/ IV STAND, 3 FUNCTION', 'jp-0212202016-Electric-Patient-Bed-with-iv-stand-3-function.png', '&lt;div&gt;Provides both safety and comfort to patients and caregivers alike, whether it is in intensive care, standard operations, in the treatment of children, or in patient transport.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;FEATURES&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Outer Dimension: 212(L) x 96(W) cm ;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Back board max. angle &ndash; 80 degrees ; Calf board max. angle &ndash; 40 degrees ; Bed Rails Height &ndash; not less than 35 cm&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bed Capacity &ndash; 135 kgs.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Collapsible Aluminum siderail&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The backboard , calf board and foot board are electrically adjusted&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Backrest function adjusted From 0&deg;to 80&deg;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Footrest function adjusted From 0&deg;to 45&deg;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Low adjusted from 450-720mm&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;It has quiet and smooth operation that provides maximum patient comfort.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Aluminum folding guard rails and pedal locking castors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Double handle knobs&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;IV Stand&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;With 3 cranks, the bed is able to perform the following base functions:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://rainbowcare.com.sg/image/catalog/products/beds/function1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Function 1&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; display: block; border-radius: 3px; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Back Raise&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;http://rainbowcare.com.sg/image/catalog/products/beds/function2.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Function 2&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; display: block; border-radius: 3px; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Leg Raise&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;http://rainbowcare.com.sg/image/catalog/products/beds/function3.jpg&quot; al