(182, 'Unomedical Guedel Airway', 'jp-0312202011-Unomedical-Guedel-Airway-PPI-Watermark.jpg', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Anatomically correct shape- follows the contour of the plate of the patient.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bite block- provides access to the suction catheter.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Color coded- for easy size identification&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Soft rounded edge- prevents damage to tissue.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 7),
(183, 'Unomedical Closed Suction System', 'jp-0712202008-Unomedical-Cathy-Closed-Suction-System-(1).jpg', '&lt;div&gt;Helps patient to clear secretion while breathing and reduce risk of oxygen desaturation. The soft sleeve isolates suction catheter from direct contact to caregivers, avoiding contamination and cross infection. Also use in aid of suctioning in intubated patients.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Features and Benefits:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Cathy reduces airborne environment bacterial contamination and subsequent health hazards.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Cathy&rsquo;s innovative design provides far greater safety and convenience for patients and healthcare staff than conventional open suction systems. Cathy&rsquo;s greatest advantage is that there is only a slight reduction of PEEP (Positive End Expiratory Pressure) during use.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Disconnecting Ring - For easy disconnection of Cathy.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Swivel Standard Connector - Fits all standard ventilator equipment.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Convenient Knob - Clearly indicates open / close position.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Built-in non-return valve in flushing port - Eliminates unwanted splashes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;The Semi-transparent Protective Sleeve - Allows easy catheter manipulation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Colour-Coded Flangers - For immediate visual identification of sizes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Clear Safety Lid - Prevents suction button from being accidentally pressed.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Built-in Filter - Reduces risk of cross-contamination when suctioning takes place.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ergonomic Design - Provides a firm yet comfortable grip on suction control.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Universal Connector - For attachment to virtually all suction tubes and sputum sample collection devices.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone  wp-image-2539&quot; src=&quot;https://pmc.ph/products/wp-content/uploads/2020/12