(184, 'Unimex Strerile Surgical Gloves', 'jp-0912202014-Unimex-Surgical-Gloves-Powder-Free-(1).jpg', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Unimex Sterile Surgical Gloves is designed to provide 2-way protection for the benefit of the patient and healthcare professionals alike during surgical operations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;FEATURES AND BENEFITS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Lightly powdered with finest talc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Tough glove yet gentle on hands&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; outline: none !important;&quot;&gt;Thin enough to provide sensitivity, thick enough to protect hands from contaminating materials&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, 18),
(185, 'CleanSpace2 Power System', 'jp-1012202012-CleanSpace-Powered-Respirator-(3).jpg', '&lt;div&gt;The CleanSpace2 Powered Respirator Unit is a battery-powered, positive pressure air-purifying/filtering respirator. This respirator is breathe responsive and is designed to provide comfortable respiratory protection against gases,vapours, bacteria, viruses and other airborne biohazards.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Features and benefits&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lightweight, comfortable and easy to wear over long periods.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Portable: no hoses, belts or waist mounted battery packs.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Efficiency Particulate Filters (Fiberglass Pleated Filter); suitable for use against solid and liquid particulates including dusts, mists, fumes, fibres, bacteria and viruses.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;AirSensit&trade; System for mask pressure control and breathe responsive airflow.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;One-button system, standby and auto-start/stop modes for quick don/doffing.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Easy to use support harness&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;With altitude compensated filter blocked detection.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Long operating time: up to 8 hours and quick battery recharging: &amp;lt; 2hours&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Can be tested by quantitatively mask fit checks (portacounts).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Compatible with all CleanSpace half masks and particulate filters.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Suitable for protection against airborne biohazards.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Visual/Audible alarms for: particulate filter end of life, battery charge level, low battery warning, manufacturers minimum design flow (120L/min).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;No servicing or maintenance required.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Made in Australia&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;Specifications&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Peak airflow: Up to 220 l/min&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Weight: 520g&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lithium-ion polymer battery&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Operating time: up to 8 hour