(188, 'Urosenz Silicone Foley Balloon Catheter', 'jp-1712202021-PPI-Urosenz-Silicone-Foley-Balloon-Catheter.jpg', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);&quot;&gt;Made from 100% silicone, biocompatible and completely inert, preventing tissue irritation and encrustation during extended period of indwelling bladder catheterization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Features and Benefits:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type: none; border-left: 3px solid rgb(221, 221, 221) !important; padding-left: 15px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;&quot;&gt;With radiopaque line and tip which allows visualization during x-ray, for placement confirmation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type: none; border-left: 3px solid rgb(221, 221, 221) !important; padding-left: 15px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;&quot;&gt;Clear design of the body and funnel allows to see potential blockage&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type: none; border-left: 3px solid rgb(221, 221, 221) !important; padding-left: 15px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;&quot;&gt;Large internal lumen for maximum drainage, less traumatization and easier expulsion of clots&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type: none; border-left: 3px solid rgb(221, 221, 221) !important; padding-left: 15px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;&quot;&gt;With balloon which provides strength, symmetry and elasticity&lt;/li&gt